          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-andrew-smith" title="Mr Andrew Smith">The Secretary of State for Work and Pensions (Mr. Andrew Smith)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">The new arrangements for child support came into operation for new cases and some linked old scheme cases from 3 March 2003. Progress has been slower than anticipated, chiefly due to problems with the new computer and telephony systems. However, over the course of the first year of operation of the new scheme, progress in performance has grown steadily. For example, more than a third of all maintenance</p><p>
